        },
        "77c3a61e-ac91-411c-8dd7-ba8d8c36f977": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "testimonial_text": "<p>The fit was perfect for everyone, and the personalization added a special touch. It was the ideal attire.<\/p>",
            "customer_name": "SOPHIA RODRIGUEZ",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "b8a1aa44-718e-4d12-9f38-3bc6acae7c29": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "testimonial_text": "<p>The quality and attention to detail were exceptional. We felt so comfortable and looked great in the photos.<\/p>",
